## Method
What you did. Which experiment, which baseline, which parameters.

## Result
What you observed. Numbers with units. Null comparison.

## Verdict
Structural? Indistinguishable? Needs more data? Failed for X reason?

## Consecutio
What this opens for the next cycle. One line.
```

Keep it under 2 pages. The morning reader is tired.

